<text><body>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0340b16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0340b17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0340b18" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1280</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0340b19" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><note n="0340001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本</note>摩醯首羅大自在天王神通化生
<lb n="0340b20" ed="T"/>伎藝天女念誦法</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0340b21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0340b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0340b2201">爾時摩醯首羅天王於大自在天上，與諸天
<lb n="0340b23" ed="T"/>女前後圍繞，神通遊戲作諸伎樂。忽然之<note n="0340002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">間＝門【甲】</note><note n="0340002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">間【大】，門【甲】</note><app n="0340002"><lem wit="【大】">間</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">門</rdg></app>
<lb n="0340b24" ed="T"/>於髮際中化出一天女，顏容端正伎藝第一，
<lb n="0340b25" ed="T"/>一切諸天無能勝者。於大眾中而作是言：「我
<lb n="0340b26" ed="T"/>今為欲利益一切，<note n="0340003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＋（情）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0340003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，有情【考偽-原】</note><app n="0340003"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">有情</rdg></app>所祈願豐饒吉祥富樂
<lb n="0340b27" ed="T"/>之事，隨心悕求悉能滿足，於諸業藝速能成
<lb n="0340b28" ed="T"/>就。我有祕密陀羅尼法要，今當說之。」即說陀
<lb n="0340b29" ed="T"/>羅尼曰：</p>
<pb n="0340c" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1280.0340c"/>
<lb n="0340c01" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0340c0101">「曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>榅支摩貌施佉地尾鉢<note n="0340004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【甲】＊</note><note n="0340004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】＊，囉【甲】＊</note><app n="0340004"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>鉢地野
<lb n="0340c02" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>試<note place="inline">引</note>迦囉者嚕啉<note place="inline">二合</note>怛儞野<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去引</note>濕
<lb n="0340c03" ed="T"/>嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>惹底<g ref="#CB00942"/>吠囉摩惹哩儞吽<note place="inline">引</note>發吒<note place="inline">半音</note>娑
<lb n="0340c04" ed="T"/>嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>」</p>
<lb n="0340c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0340c0501">是時眾伎藝天女說此陀羅尼已，告諸天眾：
<lb n="0340c06" ed="T"/>「若欲誦持我此陀羅尼者，先須建立道場，如
<lb n="0340c07" ed="T"/>法嚴飾，種種香花以為供養。於二七日或一
<lb n="0340c08" ed="T"/>七日，受持齋戒，斷其婬欲，誦此陀羅尼滿<note n="0340005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其萬遍＝足五百遍ィ【原】</note><note n="0340005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其萬遍【大】，足五百遍【校異-原】</note><app n="0340005"><lem wit="【大】">其
<lb n="0340c09" ed="T"/>萬遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">足五百遍</rdg></app>或十萬遍。於其中間勿食酒肉薰穢，至
<lb n="0340c10" ed="T"/>心誦持，天女現前種種加備，一切願求皆悉
<lb n="0340c11" ed="T"/>滿足，從此已後無有障礙。乃至妻子薰穢亦
<lb n="0340c12" ed="T"/>不制斷，若能淨持最為速驗，後有所用應<note n="0340006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝合【甲】</note><note n="0340006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令【大】，合【甲】</note><app n="0340006"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合</rdg></app>
<lb n="0340c13" ed="T"/>成就。</p>
<lb n="0340c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0340c1401">「若持誦時先須結界，或水或灰加持七遍，散
<lb n="0340c15" ed="T"/>灑四方，隨心遠近即成結界地，一切鬼神莫
<lb n="0340c16" ed="T"/>能博近。若誦至一千遍，能令天龍人及非人
<lb n="0340c17" ed="T"/>見即歡喜。若誦至二千遍，一切鬼神皆悉衛
<lb n="0340c18" ed="T"/>護。若誦至三千遍，<note n="0340007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">草藥＝藥草【甲】</note><note n="0340007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">草藥【大】，藥草【甲】</note><app n="0340007"><lem wit="【大】">草藥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">藥草</rdg></app>精靈悉現其前，華
<lb n="0340c19" ed="T"/>菓林神歡喜隨從。若誦至四千遍，一切毘多
<lb n="0340c20" ed="T"/>羅鬼深生恭敬。若誦至五千遍，一切龍神眷
<lb n="0340c21" ed="T"/>屬男女歡喜敬仰愛念無厭。若誦至六千遍，
<lb n="0340c22" ed="T"/>一切藥叉眷屬男女歡喜隨<note n="0340008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逐＝遂【甲】＊</note><note n="0340008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">逐【大】＊，遂【甲】＊</note><app n="0340008"><lem wit="【大】">逐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">遂</rdg></app>，任其所使。若
<lb n="0340c23" ed="T"/>誦至七千遍，一切天王摩達嚕等并其眷屬
<lb n="0340c24" ed="T"/>以給侍，種種驅役不以為倦。若誦至八千遍，
<lb n="0340c25" ed="T"/>一切持明五通仙人等深生歡喜仰無盡。若
<lb n="0340c26" ed="T"/>誦滿一萬遍乃至十萬遍，一切天、龍、藥叉、乾
<lb n="0340c27" ed="T"/>闥婆、阿修<note n="0340009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＋（迦樓羅）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0340009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】，羅迦樓羅【考偽-原】</note><app n="0340009"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">羅迦樓羅</rdg></app>、緊那羅、摩呼羅伽、人非人等，乃
<lb n="0340c28" ed="T"/>至塞乾陀天一切鬼神，生大歡喜，隨<app type="star" corresp="#0340008"><lem wit="【大】">逐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">遂</rdg></app>侍衛，
<lb n="0340c29" ed="T"/>常令行者豐饒吉祥。</p>
<pb n="0341a" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1280.0341a"/>
<lb n="0341a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341a0101">「又法若欲<note n="0341001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祈＋（雨）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0341001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祈【大】，祈雨【考偽-原】</note><app n="0341001"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">祈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">祈雨</rdg></app>止，不以為難。若天<note n="0341002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">旱＝早【甲】</note><note n="0341002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">旱【大】，早【甲】</note><app n="0341002"><lem wit="【大】">旱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">早</rdg></app>時，如法
<lb n="0341a02" ed="T"/>結界壇，護摩念誦，誦此真言滿一萬遍，其雨
<lb n="0341a03" ed="T"/>應時即下。若雨過多惡欲止者，加持淨灰一
<lb n="0341a04" ed="T"/>百八遍，空中擲之，其雨即止。</p>
<lb n="0341a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341a0501">「又法若有怨家興起惡意，以用朱砂或其赤
<lb n="0341a06" ed="T"/>土，書名或<note n="0341003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">書＝畫ヵ【原】＊</note><note n="0341003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">書【大】＊，畫【考偽-原】＊</note><app n="0341003"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">書</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">畫</rdg></app>形，於左脚下踏之念誦，夜後
<lb n="0341a07" ed="T"/>作之，一百八遍，無問遠近彼怨自來求解怨
<lb n="0341a08" ed="T"/>結，心生和順轉生<note n="0341004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愛＝恭【甲】</note><note n="0341004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愛【大】，恭【甲】</note><app n="0341004"><lem wit="【大】">愛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">恭</rdg></app>敬。</p>
<lb n="0341a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341a0901">「又法若欲使役一切鬼神，<note n="0341005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＝先【甲】</note><note n="0341005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆【大】，先【甲】</note><app n="0341005"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">先</rdg></app>當召集，生<note n="0341006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愍＝敏【甲】</note><note n="0341006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愍【大】，敏【甲】</note><app n="0341006"><lem wit="【大】">愍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">敏</rdg></app>
<lb n="0341a10" ed="T"/>念心，隨分飲食加持一百八遍而散施之，然
<lb n="0341a11" ed="T"/>後驅使，速疾成<note n="0341a1101" resp="CBETA" type="add">辦【CB】，辨【大】</note><app n="0341a1101"><lem resp="CBETA" wit="【CB】">辦</lem><rdg wit="【大】">辨</rdg></app>，常生歡喜終不離人。</p>
<lb n="0341a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341a1201">「又法若欲鉤召一切人民，隨心所念無問遠
<lb n="0341a13" ed="T"/>近，加持水七遍散於四方，望彼稱誦一百八
<lb n="0341a14" ed="T"/>遍，無問識與不識悉來奔就，隨心所為不敢
<lb n="0341a15" ed="T"/>違<note n="0341007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逆＝迸【甲】</note><note n="0341007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">逆【大】，迸【甲】</note><app n="0341007"><lem wit="【大】">逆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">迸</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0341a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341a1601">「又法若有怨家來欲相害，至心誦明一百八
<lb n="0341a17" ed="T"/>遍，彼即被打身<note n="0341008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">契＝熱【甲】</note><note n="0341008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">契【大】，熱【甲】</note><app n="0341008"><lem wit="【大】">契</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">熱</rdg></app>如火。若迴心相伏，即與
<lb n="0341a18" ed="T"/>解之，時誦明七遍云放即放，其身即平復如
<lb n="0341a19" ed="T"/>本。</p>
<lb n="0341a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341a2001">「又法若有夫婦外心相背不相喜見，猶如<note n="0341009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">火水＝水火【甲】</note><note n="0341009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">火水【大】，水火【甲】</note><app n="0341009"><lem wit="【大】">火
<lb n="0341a21" ed="T"/>水</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">水火</rdg></app>相憎者，密書其名勿令知覺，一依前法左
<lb n="0341a22" ed="T"/>脚踏之，稱名誦一千八遍，即相和順轉相怜
<lb n="0341a23" ed="T"/>愛如同膠<note n="0341010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漆＝染【甲】</note><note n="0341010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漆【大】，染【甲】</note><app n="0341010"><lem wit="【大】">漆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">染</rdg></app>，永更不生憎背之意。</p>
<lb n="0341a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341a2401">「又法若有所愛<note n="0341011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宣＝寡ヵ【原】</note><note n="0341011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宣【大】，寡【考偽-原】</note><app n="0341011"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">宣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">寡</rdg></app>婦，乃至諸天<note n="0341012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女婇＝婇女【甲】</note><note n="0341012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">女婇【大】，婇女【甲】</note><app n="0341012"><lem wit="【大】">女婇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婇女</rdg></app>及天
<lb n="0341a25" ed="T"/>帝釋妃后眷屬心所愛者，一依前法念誦召
<lb n="0341a26" ed="T"/>之，應時即至自來求之請為給<note n="0341013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝待【甲】</note><note n="0341013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍【大】，待【甲】</note><app n="0341013"><lem wit="【大】">侍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">待</rdg></app>。若不<note n="0341014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">違＝遣【甲】</note><note n="0341014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">違【大】，遣【甲】</note><app n="0341014"><lem wit="【大】">違</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">遣</rdg></app>
<lb n="0341a27" ed="T"/>之，終不捨離。</p>
<lb n="0341a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341a2801">「又法若欲鉤召藥叉女等求其財寶，隨心召
<lb n="0341a29" ed="T"/>之迅疾即至，一切所須悉皆奉獻，請為妻妾
<pb n="0341b" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1280.0341b"/>
<lb n="0341b01" ed="T"/>或為給侍。</p>
<lb n="0341b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341b0201">「又法若欲得一切貴人愛敬，稱名念誦一千
<lb n="0341b03" ed="T"/>八遍，自來歸敬以為僕使。</p>
<lb n="0341b04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341b0401">「又法若入官府，至心誦明七遍而至，遙仰善
<lb n="0341b05" ed="T"/>相<note n="0341015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">使＝便【甲】</note><note n="0341015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">使【大】，便【甲】</note><app n="0341015"><lem wit="【大】">使</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">便</rdg></app>得隨心。若見面時喜悅無量，有事求之
<lb n="0341b06" ed="T"/>即能相為。</p>
<lb n="0341b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341b0701">「又法若有所愛女人或其男子意相<note n="0341016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樂＝著【甲】</note><note n="0341016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樂【大】，著【甲】</note><app n="0341016"><lem wit="【大】">樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">著</rdg></app>者，以
<lb n="0341b08" ed="T"/>加持胡燕脂或紅藍花汁，塗其二脚掌下，以
<lb n="0341b09" ed="T"/>火炙之，二手掩上，稱名念誦，彼即立至，自來
<lb n="0341b10" ed="T"/>相求，乃至深隱之處直來相<note n="0341017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔來〕－【甲】</note><note n="0341017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0341017"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>見，乃至命終
<lb n="0341b11" ed="T"/>不肯相捨<note place="inline">每稱名時於娑婆二合賀句上加之，除其發吒二字</note>。若是女人為求
<lb n="0341b12" ed="T"/>男子者，並依前法作之，隨心即至。</p>
<lb n="0341b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341b1301">「又法若欲得令見諸鬼神身者，取尸陀林燒
<lb n="0341b14" ed="T"/>死人柴護摩，一明一燒乃至一百八遍，一切
<lb n="0341b15" ed="T"/>鬼神悉自現身，即得相見。</p>
<lb n="0341b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341b1601">「又法若<note n="0341018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＋（人）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0341018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，有人【考偽-原】</note><app n="0341018"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">有人</rdg></app>所<note n="0341019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝求【甲】</note><note n="0341019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，求【甲】</note><app n="0341019"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">求</rdg></app>一切財寶，隨心所須，至心
<lb n="0341b17" ed="T"/>持誦自然獲得。</p>
<lb n="0341b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341b1801">「又法若欲縛人問事，無問大小淨與不淨，心
<lb n="0341b19" ed="T"/>想本尊至心念誦，應時即縛，問知三世之事，
<lb n="0341b20" ed="T"/>一切皆說無所不知。非但能縛一人，乃至百
<lb n="0341b21" ed="T"/>千萬人，至心誦之，隨心應念一時即縛。</p>
<lb n="0341b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341b2201">「又法若有家人逃走極遠處去者，準前書名，
<lb n="0341b23" ed="T"/>踏之念誦，其<note n="0341020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝十【甲】</note><note n="0341020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，十【甲】</note><app n="0341020"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">十</rdg></app>迴還奔走立至。若來遲者，即
<lb n="0341b24" ed="T"/>以灰<anchor xml:id="fxT21p0341b01"/>書彼形，每日三時作法，每誦真言一遍
<lb n="0341b25" ed="T"/>打之一下，乃至三七遍已，彼即恐怖，如風即
<lb n="0341b26" ed="T"/>至。</p>
<lb n="0341b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341b2701">「又法若欲療治一切病者，取佉陀羅木截作
<lb n="0341b28" ed="T"/>二十一段，誦明一投火中燒之。遍已，但是疾
<lb n="0341b29" ed="T"/>病即得除差。</p>
<pb n="0341c" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1280.0341c"/>
<lb n="0341c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c0101">「又法若有患神病者，取阿魏藥、安悉香、雄黃、
<lb n="0341c02" ed="T"/>白芥子、青木香、<note n="0341021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝苦ヵ【原】</note><note n="0341021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，苦【考偽-原】</note><app n="0341021"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">苦</rdg></app>練葉等，並擣<note n="0341022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">節＝篩【甲】</note><note n="0341022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">節【大】，篩【甲】</note><app n="0341022"><lem wit="【大】">節</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">篩</rdg></app>相和作
<lb n="0341c03" ed="T"/>四十九丸，一誦明一投火中，其病即差。</p>
<lb n="0341c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c0401">「又法若患狐魅病者，取雄黃、白芥子、芎藭、獨
<lb n="0341c05" ed="T"/>頭萩、犀角、羖羊尿、白馬懸蹄、驢馬夜眼，並擣
<lb n="0341c06" ed="T"/>篩為丸，加持一百八遍，燒薰鼻孔之中并塗
<lb n="0341c07" ed="T"/>身上，狐魅消滅，其病即差。</p>
<lb n="0341c08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c0801">「如上所說利益之法悉皆神驗，速疾成就。凡
<lb n="0341c09" ed="T"/>欲作法必須至誠，若不至心、輕慢，誦者無益，
<lb n="0341c10" ed="T"/>法亦不成。若至誠心，一遍便獲効驗。我今略
<lb n="0341c11" ed="T"/>說少耳，餘法莫能窮盡。若欲持誦求其證驗，
<lb n="0341c12" ed="T"/>先畫我壇并畫我像安置壇中，如法供養，即
<lb n="0341c13" ed="T"/>疾證驗，即疾成就。」</p>
<lb n="0341c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c1401">「大自在天女畫像法：</p>
<lb n="0341c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c1501">「先畫摩醯首羅天王，三面六臂，顏貌奇特，端
<lb n="0341c16" ed="T"/>正可畏。從其髮際化生一天女，殊妙可喜，天
<lb n="0341c17" ed="T"/>上人間無能勝者。著天衣服，瓔珞嚴身，兩手
<lb n="0341c18" ed="T"/>腕上各有鐶釧，左手向上捧一天花、右手向
<lb n="0341c19" ed="T"/>下作捻裙勢。身形可長三尺，或隨大小任取
<lb n="0341c20" ed="T"/>稱量。畫像了已，如法安置壇中供養。」</p>
<lb n="0341c21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c2101">「祈願壇法：</p>
<lb n="0341c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c2201">「量高四指肘量，隨其處所大小。壇開四門，於東
<lb n="0341c23" ed="T"/>門內燒<note n="0341023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">安悉香＝香安悉【甲】</note><note n="0341023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">安悉香【大】，香安悉【甲】</note><app n="0341023"><lem wit="【大】">安悉香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">香安悉</rdg></app>，南門內燒沈水香，西門燒薰
<lb n="0341c24" ed="T"/>陸香，北門燒兜樓婆香。於壇中心安本尊像。
<lb n="0341c25" ed="T"/>於四角安刀一口，懸明鏡。於四門各須安箭
<lb n="0341c26" ed="T"/>兩隻。於南門兩邊安尾那夜迦位。於壇四緣
<lb n="0341c27" ed="T"/>周迴，隨其力分安置甜脆華果等以為供養。」</p>
<lb n="0341c28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c2801">「次說火壇法：</p>
<lb n="0341c29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0341c2901">「作護摩爐深十二指，爐可橫量一肘。於壇傍
<pb n="0342a" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1280.0342a"/>
<lb n="0342a01" ed="T"/>作彼怨家形貌，以刀<note n="0342001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之割＝割之【甲】</note><note n="0342001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之割【大】，割之【甲】</note><app n="0342001"><lem wit="【大】">之割</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">割之</rdg></app>，護摩念誦，以用皂
<lb n="0342a02" ed="T"/>夾刺柴燒諸毒藥，一誦明一燒之，滿四十九
<lb n="0342a03" ed="T"/>遍或一百八遍，即大驗耳，彼怨家即便消滅。
<lb n="0342a04" ed="T"/>若療一切疾病，亦如上法。作彼鬼神形狀，斷
<lb n="0342a05" ed="T"/>截燒之，決死之病應時得愈。」</p>
<lb n="0342a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342a0601">「摩醯首羅大自在天神通遊戲變化頂生眾伎
<lb n="0342a07" ed="T"/>藝天女成就法印。</p>
<lb n="0342a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342a0801">「二手合掌，二<note n="0342002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（無）＋名【甲】</note><note n="0342002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名【大】，無名【甲】</note><app n="0342002"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">無名</rdg></app>指二中指外相叉指面著其
<lb n="0342a09" ed="T"/>手背，二頭指微蹙頭似寶，二大指頭並來去
<lb n="0342a10" ed="T"/>即成。誦請召明曰：</p>
<lb n="0342a11" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0342a1101">「曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>摩醯濕嚩<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="star" corresp="#0340004"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note>　榅支摩冒<note place="inline">引</note>試
<lb n="0342a12" ed="T"/>佉野<note n="0342003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曀＝<g ref="#CB14631"/>【甲】</note><note n="0342003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曀【大】，<g ref="#CB14631"/>【甲】</note><app n="0342003"><lem wit="【大】">曀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><g ref="#CB14631"/></rdg></app>醯<note place="inline">去引</note>呬娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>」</p>
<lb n="0342a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342a1301">「結此印已，隨誦此明七遍，請召本天與諸眷
<lb n="0342a14" ed="T"/>屬悉皆降至，種種加備。</p>
<lb n="0342a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342a1501">「次結神通攝召一切印。以右手中指直竪，次
<lb n="0342a16" ed="T"/>以名指苾在中指後，以頭指鉤召指頭，以大
<lb n="0342a17" ed="T"/>指橫押頭小二指甲，以中指如鉤勢向外鉤
<lb n="0342a18" ed="T"/>向身來<note n="0342004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【甲】</note><note n="0342004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0342004"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>即是。誦根本明，於娑嚩<note place="inline">二<note n="0342005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（引）【甲】</note><note n="0342005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合引【甲】</note><app n="0342005"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合引</rdg></app></note>賀字
<lb n="0342a19" ed="T"/>上加所召者名請之。</p>
<lb n="0342a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342a2001">「若結此印誦明，攝召一切悉皆立至。是神通
<lb n="0342a21" ed="T"/>攝召印亦通一切處用。</p>
<lb n="0342a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342a2201">「若逢<note n="0342006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怨＋（家）【甲】</note><note n="0342006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怨【大】，怨家【甲】</note><app n="0342006"><lem wit="【大】">怨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">怨家</rdg></app>惡人欲相<note n="0342007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">刑＝形【甲】</note><note n="0342007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">刑【大】，形【甲】</note><app n="0342007"><lem wit="【大】">刑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">形</rdg></app>害，結印展其中指，望
<lb n="0342a23" ed="T"/>彼撝之，自然散壞。諸惡鬼神，指之消滅。</p>
<lb n="0342a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342a2401">「結此印誦根本明，印心、額、喉、頂即成護身，一
<lb n="0342a25" ed="T"/>切鬼魅不敢親近。其法必須從師親授，淨室
<lb n="0342a26" ed="T"/>密持。每念誦了，以淨繒帛覆天形像，不得輒
<lb n="0342a27" ed="T"/>說此法向餘人，若妄泄之終身無効。慎之慎
<lb n="0342a28" ed="T"/>之。</p>
<lb n="0342a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342a2901">「其天像或畫或素總得。於壇中心安置本天
<pb n="0342b" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1280.0342b"/>
<lb n="0342b01" ed="T"/>形像，於天左右各安二女天，若壇中安坐位，
<lb n="0342b02" ed="T"/>形貌可喜，如天女形狀。其像後又置二侍從
<lb n="0342b03" ed="T"/>女天位，唯於前面留火爐處所，燒諸香藥奉
<lb n="0342b04" ed="T"/>獻本天。如不能安火爐，著一寶盆，盛其香水
<lb n="0342b05" ed="T"/>著諸妙花獻之亦得。於壇四角四門不能安
<lb n="0342b06" ed="T"/>其刀箭，但於壇外畫之亦得。唯移鏡安於壇
<lb n="0342b07" ed="T"/>內四角，如餘部壇法安羯磨杵處即得仰安
<lb n="0342b08" ed="T"/>之。</p>
<lb n="0342b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0342b0901">「若畫壇時，於壇四面地上畫作五色<note n="0342008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綵＝彩ヵ【原】</note><note n="0342008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綵【大】，彩【考偽-原】</note><app n="0342008"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">綵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">彩</rdg></app>雲，如
<lb n="0342b10" ed="T"/>捧壇從地踴出勢。」</p>
<lb n="0342b11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>摩醯首羅頂生天女<note n="0342009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本奧書曰長慶元年三月鬼宿直日傳五部瑜伽全真本記</note>法</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
